 "versionId": "f768619a-f296-4f35-99a0-fd8c6e1900ee", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.3277, "width": 0.777, "height": 0.20689999999999997}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.3277}, {"x": 0.8879, "y": 0.3277}, {"x": 0.8879, "y": 0.5346}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.5346}], "comment": "The analysis would benefit from referencing external corroborative sources (e.g. archival records, testimonies) to demonstrate how historians verify the diary\u00e2\u0080\u0099s reliability.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": null}, {"id": "49287bb5-208e-4158-a9c2-9e65ccbbc26d", "versionId": "f768619a-f296-4f35-99a0-fd8c6e1900ee", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.3385, "width": 0.7776, "height": 0.20740000000000003}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.3385}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.3385}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.5459}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.5459}], "comment": "References to audits, recounts and court orders remain vague; naming specific reports or jurisdictions would anchor the analysis in concrete evidence and deepen the justification.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": null}, {"id": "77d60846-9c23-4907-83f1-0b87c0381c12", "versionId": "f768619a-f296-4f35-99a0-fd8c6e1900ee", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.5478, "width": 0.7776, "height": 0.268}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.5478}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.5478}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.8158}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8158}], "comment": "Assertions about leadership and trust are made without connecting to TOK concepts of authority or expert knowledge, reducing analytical precision.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": null}, {"id": "42e4130a-280e-4f73-b74d